    This class specifies the audio data format based on 3 parameters: the number of bytes per sample, the sampling rate, and number of channels.

    The GNAudioSourceMic class manages resources for applications to stream audio from the platform's audio input hardware.
    GNConfig

    GNCoverArt
    Container class for album cover art.
